snippet: Alison Lee shot a six-under-par 65 on Thursday for a share of the first-round lead in the L.P.G.A. Malaysia in Kuala Lumpur.
abstract: Alison Lee shoots six-under-par 65 to share lead at LPGA Malaysia tournament with Xi Yu Lin; other golf results noted.
